<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634128198660265789" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634128199560740302">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The demonstrated <em>TreeView </em>supports keyboard navigation. Use keyboard navigation keys for moving through tree nodes. </p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>TreeView </em>supports manipulation with the keyboard. The <em>UP </em>and <em>DOWN ARROW</em> keys provide a means of moving up and down the <em>TreeView</em>. The <em>LEFT </em>and <em>RIGHT ARROW</em> keys collapse and expand the nodes in the <em>TreeView</em>. The <em>ARROW </em>keys provide selecting node on the TreeView.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
